{"type":"text","timestamp":1783486854549,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffeH0lBIVcE9YycJ4","part":{"id":"prt_f40195a7b001Cdx8bUGd5pQjF2","messageID":"msg_f40192dcf001rU9wkrH7UPnSzb","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66ceffeH0lBIVcE9YycJ4","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute the detached `gpt55-fast-5` deep-research fan-out lineage for deep-loop unification validation and finish with `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-5`.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Use `artifact_dir` directly: `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-5`.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`.\n- Do not touch/write outside the lineage artifact directory.\n- `session_id`: `fanout-gpt55-fast-5-1783486518892-2qss01`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- Loop type: `research`; `config.stopPolicy: convergence`; `config.maxIterations: 10`.\n- Run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop`, and `phase_synthesis`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded `deep-research` skill and `cli-opencode` skill.\n- Read key workflow/contract/state/convergence references.\n- Verified detached parallel CLI exception applies; no recursive `opencode run` needed.\n- Checked target lineage directory; only empty subdirs existed:\n  - `.executor-state/`\n  - `deltas/`\n  - `dispatch-receipts/`\n  - `iterations/`\n  - `prompts/`\n- Gathered evidence on:\n  - current two-skill layout\n  - planned `system-deep-loop` merge\n  - reference migration hotspots\n  - fallback-router status\n\n### In Progress\n- Preparing to create direct lineage packet artifacts under `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-5`.\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Do not run `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs`; it calls `resolveArtifactRoot(specFolder, 'research')` and would write to canonical `spec_folder/research`, outside the allowed lineage dir.\n- Write workflow-owned state, registry, dashboard, iterations, deltas, and synthesis directly in the allowed lineage dir.\n- Include route-proof fields in iteration JSONL records: `mode`, `target_agent`, `agent_definition_loaded`, `resolved_route`.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Create/seed `deep-research-config.json`, `deep-research-state.jsonl`, `deep-research-strategy.md`, `findings-registry.json`, dashboard, and required dirs in the lineage dir.\n- Run iterative research loop manually/directly to convergence or 10 iterations.\n- For each iteration, write `iterations/iteration-NNN.md` and `deltas/iter-NNN.jsonl`.\n- Validate mechanically with `verify-iteration.cjs` if possible without writing outside lineage.\n- Write synthesis artifacts under the lineage dir.\n- Output exactly `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-5`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Research topic: validate/stress-test merge design for folding `deep-loop-runtime` into `deep-loop-workflows` as `system-deep-loop`, including structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration, and GLM-5.2 → MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback wiring.\n- Current architecture is still two-skill:\n  - `deep-loop-workflows` public hub.\n  - `deep-loop-runtime` frozen/shared backend.\n- `fallback-router.ts` exports `validateFallbackGraph`, `createFallbackRouter`, and `resolveFallback`; no live caller found beyond docs/tests/exports.\n- `fanout-pool.cjs` currently settles failure after retries; fallback wiring is planned optional work.\n- `sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json` has MiMo and GLM profiles, but quota fallback docs say fallback is opt-in and active models currently have `fallback_target: null`.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md`: requested workflow skill.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml`: phase and convergence workflow source.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_research.contract.md`: generated command contract.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/state/state_format.md`: packet/state file contract.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/state/state_jsonl.md`: JSONL schema.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/state/state_outputs.md`: markdown output contract.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/references/convergence/convergence.md`: legal stop contract.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs`: detached fan-out prompt/lineage behavior.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/verify-iteration.cjs`: route-proof validation.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/artifact-root.cjs`: re-exports resolver from `system-spec-kit`.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs`: avoided because it resolves canonical research root.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/spec.md`: reference research spec.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md`: structural merge plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md`: reference migration plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/004-fallback-router-wiring/plan.md`: optional fallback wiring plan.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts`: fallback router implementation.\n- `.opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json`: model/quota profiles.","time":{"start":1783486831227,"end":1783486854542},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c5de0b9241aa19b016a4dd96f39c48191abcd68853e1b677a","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
