:\"Third pass expanded beyond command YAML into advisor projections, tests, agents, system-spec-kit integrations, and sk-doc examples.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Is child 003 broad enough for non-code references and generated routing projections?\",\"Which migration stages are most likely to leave stale old-skill names?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Is child 003 broad enough for non-code references and generated routing projections?\",\"Which migration stages are most likely to leave stale old-skill names?\"],\"findingDetails\":[{\"id\":\"G55F5-F009\",\"title\":\"Reference migration must be dependency ordered; no safe moved-but-unrewritten intermediate state exists\",\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:42\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:66\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:71\"]},{\"id\":\"G55F5-F010\",\"title\":\"Advisor code, generated projections, hardcoded tests, and divergence ledgers are migration-critical, not prose cleanup\",\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:75\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:84\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:101\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tests/routing-parity-deep-skills.vitest.ts:30\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/tests/routing-parity-deep-skills.vitest.ts:62\"]},{\"id\":\"G55F5-F011\",\"title\":\"Command contract migration spans source YAML, router markdown, and regenerated compiled outputs\",\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:89\",\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop